divs: Sighting DetailsWe (my wife and I) were outside when a commercial jet flying overhead drew our attention. We noticed another object in the vicinity, but lower and slower than the airliner. The airliner had left our field of view by this time. Object was cylindrical, blunt on both ends and what caught our eye was that it had no wings or fins. It was white with a large red stripe around its' midsection. Again, NO sound. By the time I went inside and got my camera, this pic was all I could get. It appeared "floating" mmore than under power, and we watched until we couldn't see it anymore. We were somewhat puzzled and skeptical about the odd shape, NO wings and NO noise. Date stamp on photo is correct, but the time appears to be incorrect as it was bright and sunny.
Summary: Commercial jet overhead drew our attention, saw cylinder nearby
